# Upstream PR sync

Read [MEMORY.md](MEMORY.md) § **Open upstream PRs** for the current PR list.

## Three layers

| Layer | Branch | Role |
|-------|--------|------|
| Distro | `envyos/main` | All features merged; **bench builds** |
| PR head | `feature/<name>` on MeshEnvy `origin` | Single feature; feeds cross-fork upstream PR |
| Upstream | `dev`, `feature/ota-lora`, etc. | PR **base** on meshcore-dev / vk496 |

## While a PR is open

- Commits **for that feature** → land on **`envyos/main`** and **`feature/<name>`**; push both.
- Commits **for a different feature** → separate branch + separate PR; never cross-contaminate.
- After upstream merge → stop pushing to `feature/<name>`; integrate base into `envyos/main`.

Full workflow: [`.cursor/skills/envyos-meshcore/SKILL.md`](../skills/envyos-meshcore/SKILL.md).
